%N A393883 O.g.f. A(x) satisfies: [x^n] exp( n^8*x - n^3*A(x) ) = 0 for n >= 1.
%H A393883 Paul D. Hanna, <a href="/A393883/b393883.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..201</a>
%e A393883 O.g.f.: A(x) = x + 3844*x^2 + 1696840596*x^3 + 11843421298181888*x^4 + 600567913457231735114000*x^5 + 143229672214318101538770307845696*x^6 + ...
%e A393883 ILLUSTRATION OF DEFINITION.
%e A393883 The table of coefficients of x^k/k! in exp( n^8*x - n^3*A(x) ) begins
%e A393883   n = 1: [1,      0,        -7688,      -10181043576, ...];
%e A393883   n = 2: [1,    248,            0,      -81478854592, ...];
%e A393883   n = 3: [1,   6534,     42485580,                 0, ...];
%e A393883   n = 4: [1,  65472,   4286090752,   279902918287872, 0, ...];
%e A393883   n = 5: [1, 390500, 152489289000, 59545044183053000, 23214878976398803336000, 0, ...]; ...
%e A393883 in which a diagonal, the coefficient of x^n in row n, is all zeros.
%e A393883 RELATED SERIES.
%e A393883 exp(A(x)) = 1 + x + 7689*x^2/2! + 10181066641*x^3/3! + 284242152057901777*x^4/4! + 72068151036861185322722241*x^5/5! + 103125364426751750402197988522653081*x^6/6! + ...
%e A393883 where [x^n] exp(n^8*x) / exp(A(x))^(n^3) = 0 for n >= 1.
%o A393883 (PARI) {a(n,p=8,q=3) = my(A=[0], m); for(i=1, n+1, m=#A; A=concat(A, 0); A[m+1] = Vec( exp(m^p*x - m^q*Ser(A)) )[m+1]/(m^q) ); polcoef( Ser(A), n)}
%o A393883 for(n=1, 15, print1(a(n,8,3), ", "))
%Y A393883 Below, sequences with the parameters (p,q) indicated have an o.g.f. F(x) satisfying [x^n] exp( n^p*x - n^q*F(x) ) = 0 for n >= 1.
